From aef100f791e7d57ebd052e1b0f9f6e4af07e273e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Sun, 28 Dec 2025 00:42:51 +1100
Subject: [PATCH 66/73] soc: cix: Add bus performance state control driver

Add driver to control CI700 (memory interconnect) and NI700 (NoC
interconnect) frequencies via SCMI performance domains.

The driver provides sysfs interface for manual frequency control:
  - /sys/devices/platform/cix_bus_ci700/cur_freq
  - /sys/devices/platform/cix_bus_ci700/available_frequencies

CI700 supports 6 OPPs: 500/750/1000/1100/1300/1500 MHz
NI700 supports 3 OPPs: 375/600/750 MHz

Enable both bus nodes in Orion O6 device tree.
